 contains between 5.1 and 19 million tons of lithium, or about 35% to 136% =
of the current U.S. lithium resource estimate. Lithium boom baby!</span></p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">If the U.S. is going to usher in a clean, renewable futu=
