buttons, typing text, and switching between windows or applications. You kn=
ow, things we mere mortals regularly do on computers. Claude is essentially=
 interpreting screenshots to understand what's on the screen and to determi=
ne how to complete given tasks.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">You don&#8217;t have t=
